{"tid":2288603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【周梓樂死因研訊】死因庭筆記：撕開傷口，重看最後軌跡","createTime":"2020-11-16T15:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T15:50:56.000Z","uid":129883,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24177f7551d14b093507db86eda881b537be37ef","tid":2288603,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E5%BA%AD%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-%E6%92%95%E9%96%8B%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3-%E9%87%8D%E7%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E8%BB%8C%E8%B7%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E7%25AD%2586%25E8%25A8%2598-%25E6%2592%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25BB%258C%25E8%25B7%25A1%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=bf2a3247\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E7%25AD%2586%25E8%25A8%2598-%25E6%2592%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25BB%258C%25E8%25B7%25A1%2F&h=dc5943aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E5%BA%AD%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-%E6%92%95%E9%96%8B%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3-%E9%87%8D%E7%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E8%BB%8C%E8%B7%A1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n對待每一條問題，他嚴謹，審慎，誠懇。下午時分，死因庭拿出數十張閉路電視的截圖，請他逐張辨認圖中人是否自己的兒子。從自己家的電梯，到商場洗手間門口，到樓下街道，到富康花園和尚德停車場之間的天橋，再到最後的停車場內⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n一個父親看著這些可能是兒子生前最後的軌跡，這樣一格一格地看著，直到故事終結。<br />\n<br />\n周爸爸仔細辨認每一張截圖，「呢個衣著同身型都似」「呢個更清楚，就係梓樂」「呢幅唔太似」「呢幅行路同姿勢就似係周梓樂」「但你話肯定，我就唔敢肯定」⋯⋯看到一個影到正面的鏡頭時，他馬上說：「呢幅係，呢幅好似佢對住屋企（聽不清）笑咁（聽不清）。」<br />\n<br />\n像父母翻看子女的相簿。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇到心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ba920f42751dff8e946c4e66ad6ce9c4bf8734","tid":2288603,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"成件事好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5143c48212285dadb3d708c343667d40beb3601","tid":2288603,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"希望快啲還返個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f861e6b85e87de1e60b28da1d8b2434f9cd988","tid":2288603,"uid":322438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9306087ef6878eb3aa63ee887ca008517d5ac00","tid":2288603,"uid":322438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dcd4152b3efca134881cd6c248b46e03bb50e7","tid":2288603,"uid":146601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"祝早日沉冤得雪"},{"pid":"fafd53c8408b1a80d3d22fc1e76134a06de1140f","tid":2288603,"uid":129883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9306087ef6878eb3aa63ee887ca008517d5ac00","tid":2288603,"uid":322438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"仲有希望快啲還原到真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9026cf19ff95f212f75a69b19bd15cd16785f92d","tid":2288603,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7dcd4152b3efca134881cd6c24